### Manual Testing

```bash
python -c "
import asyncio
from youtube_dlp_server.helper import extract_video_info
async def test():
    info = await extract_video_info('https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ')
    print(f'âœ… Video: {info[\"title\"]}')
asyncio.run(test())
"
```

